## 📦 Endpoints

### Auth
- POST /auth/register  
- POST /auth/login  

### Movies
- GET /movies  
- POST /movies  
- GET /movies/:id  
- PUT /movies/:id  
- DELETE /movies/:id  

### Upload
- POST /upload  

